- 10 x 15 ft
- tomatoes:
	- one stick of wood
	- one tomato plant on either side
	- 

Tilling soil
- do it in the fall
- bout 1-1.5ft to till

Basil
- cut off a significant portion
- place in a cup of water, wait for roots
- replant

washing greens
- fill two pails with water, one handful of salt
- mix and leave for a few minutes
- place in the other water to fully clean